narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would definitely recommend this class. I thought it was very interesting and well-thought-out.

I would absolutely recommend this class if someone has any interest in early modern England. It's an amazing opportunity to learn about one subject (women) in depth, in a time period where the historiography is constantly changing.

I would definitely recommend it if you are interested in the time period and the study of women in general. The final essay gives you the chance to focus on a topic of interest, and the discussion is always interesting in class.
